charges.charge_description: 21:841(a)(1) and 21:841(b)(1)(B) POSSESSION WITH INTENT TO DISTRIBUTE 50 GRAMS OR MORE OF METHAMPHETAMINE MIXTURE(1)

charges.charge_disposition: Defendant pleaded guilty to count I of the Indictment and is committed to the custody of the United States Bureau of Prisons for a term of sixty-three (63) months (to be served concurrent to any state related charges); supervised release for a term of four (4) years; $100 special assessment.
